title: Paulson disputes Fla. Dems mailer in Orlando mayoral race
text: A mailer in Orlando's mayoral race, paid for by the�Florida Democratic Party, paints challenger Paul Paulson as an enemy of Hispanics, same-sex marriage�and an increased minimum wage, but leaves unclear the basis for those claims.� The pro-Dyer mailer's description of Paulson reads as follows: ... ...
